    <abstract>
      <t>&lt;p&gt;This document describes the Basic Mode of Layer 1 VPNs (L1VPNs).  L1VPN Basic Mode (L1VPN BM) is a port-based VPN.  In L1VPN Basic Mode, the basic unit of service is a Label Switched Path (LSP) between a pair of customer ports within a given VPN port topology.  This document defines the operational model using either provisioning or a VPN auto-discovery mechanism, and the signaling extensions for the L1VPN BM. [STANDARDS-TRACK]&lt;/p&gt;</t>
